## API Reference

| Verb | Endpoint | Description | SuccessÂ Code |
|------|----------|-------------|--------------|
| GET  | `/movie` | List all movies | **200** |
| GET  | `/movie/<id>` | Retrieve single movie | **200** (or **404** if not found) |
| POST | `/movie` | Add new movie (JSON body) | **200** â€“ returns full list incl. new item |
| PUT  | `/movie/<id>` | Replace movie by ID | **200** |
| DELETE | `/movie/<id>` | Delete movie by ID | **204** |

All responses are JSON except `DELETEÂ 204` which has an empty body.

**Example Payload**

```json
{
  "name": "Inception",
  "genre": "sci-fi",
  "length": 148
}
```

